On the abortion issue, I am still very torn. Personally, I do not think I could ever do it, but I have never been a situation that calls for it. (And I hope I never am). I can see it it certain situations (13yo girl is raped by father for example... or anyone who is raped for that matter), but as a form of &quot;Birth Control&quot; I strongly disagree. I have been told that that makes me prochoice, but in my own head, I am not sure.<br>
