ed to be more responsible when it came to both sex and respect from men.  I fell in love with this guy, and it clouded my judgement.  I also wasn't premiscuous, and I was a pretty good kid overall.  Having an abortion would have been devastating to me, I especially know that now that I have experienced a miscarriage, but having that child would have been more devastating, and I wouldn't have the life I do right now, nor would that child have the advantages my son has right now.  <br>
